name: SecCredentialType
desc: The credential type to be returned by SecKeyGetCredentials.

items.name: case `default`
items.desc: The default setting for determining whether to present UI is used.

items.name: case withUI
items.desc: Keychain operations on keys that have this credential are allowed to present UI if required.

items.name: case noUI
items.desc: Keychain operations on keys that have this credential are not allowed to present UI, and will fail if UI is required.
